# What NOT to upload to Vercel.
# When this file exists, Vercel uses it INSTEAD of .gitignore. So we must explicitly
# list every exclusion here — and crucially, we do NOT list data/questions.json
# or data/explanations.json, so the full question bank gets deployed (unlike on
# GitHub where .gitignore keeps them private).

# Source materials and build inputs
sources/
tools/
docs/
*.docx
*.doc
*.pdf
*.md
!README.md

# Sample data — production has the real files
data/questions.sample.json
data/explanations.sample.json

# Dev / OS / editor cruft
/tmp/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# Local-only directories
.claude/
.github/
